action.text:
When The New York Times drew a line in the sand on AI, it sent ripples through the entire media industry.

Meredith Kopit Levien, President & CEO of @nytimes, sat down with @robertsafian, host of @rapidresponseshow, at Masters of Scale Summit to break down the tough calls media leaders face: protecting intellectual property while adapting to technological change.

The full conversation with @mastersofscale dives into what sustainable AI practices actually look like in modern journalism.

Link in bio.

#AI #journalism #media #tech #leadership #business #innovation #NewYorkTimes #MastersOfScale
